      "dateCreated": "2026-03-23",
      "description": "Identifies high-frequency aptamer candidate sequences from paired-end FASTQ files produced by SELEX experiments. The pipeline performs overlap-based read joining, nested pattern-based filtering (Selection → 1st Sort → 2nd Sort), and outputs only the final ranked aptamer candidates (results.tsv) and a per-stage summary.",
